// @error annotate a return type
// BASE-CASE-LESS inferred cycle (A17). `ping` and `pong` call each other with no
// concrete return path anywhere in the group, so there is nothing for inference
// to latch onto — the return holes stay `Unknown`. This is a genuine limitation
